# Baloa - Football Tournament Management Platform

## Project Overview
Comprehensive platform for managing football tournaments with interactive user flows.

### Key Technologies
- React.js
- Redux
- CSS3
- Figma Design Implementation

### User Flows
- Tournament Registration
- Team Management
- Match Scheduling
- Real-time Scoring

### Project Structure
```
baloa/
├── src/
│   ├── components/
│   ├── redux/
│   ├── styles/
│   └── utils/
└── designs/
```
